.TH JJ-STARSHIP 1
.SH NAME
jj-starship \- unified Git and Jujutsu Starship prompt module
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B jj-starship
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.br
.B jj-starship
.B detect
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B jj-starship
prints prompt metadata for Git and Jujutsu repositories in a format intended
for Starship custom modules.
.PP
Use
.B jj-starship detect
as a Starship
.B when
command to check whether the current directory is inside a supported
repository.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --cwd PATH
Read repository state from PATH instead of the current directory.
.TP
.B --no-color
Disable ANSI color output.
.TP
.B --no-symbol
Hide the repository symbol prefix.
.TP
.B --help
Show upstream command help.
.TP
.B --version
Show upstream version information.
.SH EXAMPLE
.nf
[custom.jj]
when = "jj-starship detect"
shell = ["jj-starship"]
format = "$output "
.fi
.SH AUTHOR
jj-starship is written by Dillon Mulroy.
